[CV-FLAGS] ODD-UNSTABLE
[D] 975058fba5806adea892e22c53688588c29c3fb6e3658cf22443dcdd xdg-desktop-portal-1.22.1.tar.gz https://github.com/flatpak/xdg-desktop-portal/archive/1.22.1/

